docs.abstract: Facebook, Microsoft and Amazon are ramping up offerings on a platform that lets people enjoy high-quality games on any device.
docs.snippet: Facebook, Microsoft and Amazon are ramping up offerings on a platform that lets people enjoy high-quality games on any device.
docs.lead_paragraph: Imagine video gamers, untethered from their computers and consoles, playing crystal-clear versions of their favorite games anywhere. They might traverse the futuristic world of the sci-fi shooter game Halo on their mobile phones while riding the subway, or dust off old MacBook computers and hop straight into the jungle of the battle arena game League of Legends.

docs.abstract: The U.S. accused China of hacking Microsoft.
docs.snippet: The U.S. accused China of hacking Microsoft.
docs.lead_paragraph: The formal accusation follows a March cyberattack that targeted Microsoft email systems used by many of the world’s largest companies, governments and military contractors. For the first time, the U.S. also accused China of paying criminal groups to conduct large-scale hackings, including ransomware attacks.
